# 🌐 Web Programming 

## 📖 Overview
This demonstrates core web programming concepts using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## 🚀 Features
- Add and delete tasks
- Persistent storage using LocalStorage
- Dynamic DOM manipulation
- Event handling

## 🛠 Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)

## 🧠 Concepts Covered
- DOM Manipulation
- Event Listeners
- Browser Storage (LocalStorage)
- Responsive UI Design

## ▶️ How to Run
1. Download or clone the repo
2. Open `index.html` in any browser

